title: Teenage Head Discography
description:
Teenage Head are from Hamilton, Ontario, Canada.  They were very popular in
Canada during the early 1980s.  They were also one of the greatest rock and 
roll bands that have ever existed.

Teenage Head (1979)
"Frantic City" (1980)
Some Kinda Fun (1982)
Tornado (1983 mini LP-as Teenage Heads)
Teenage Head In An Endless Party - Live (1984)
Trouble In The Jungle (1985)
Electric Guitar (1988)
Head Disorder (1996)
Teenage Head With Marky Ramone (2008)
